    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Swing by and see it for yourself\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
