    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like gloss and zero rock chips or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple leather seats with no bolster wear, original factory scent, and high-resolution displays that remain crystal clear. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard, backed by a comprehensive service history from certified specialists. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its model. Perfect for the buyer who accepts nothing less than showroom perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
